{"tid":2234322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港人會輸？","createTime":"2020-10-07T22:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T01:12:45.000Z","uid":191338,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd406dfefd26d3d118ba3660c574629449afe118","tid":2234322,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T22:36:02.000Z","msg":"因為香港人太醒<br />\n算死草<br />\n個個精過鬼<br />\n做野有底線<br />\n所以同係香港人嘅政權<br />\n都知道你班友嘅底線係邊<br />\n要搵食就係香港人嘅春袋<br />\n長期冇收入去抗爭嘅代價<br />\n1％都冇<br />\n運用軍權，增加軍備，以絕對武力輾壓<br />\n明查暗訪日益削弱呢1％令港共懼怕嘅力量<br />\n香港嘅反抗勢力自己會係內鬥內哄中潰不成軍<br />\n不攻自破，不日瓦解<br />\n激活潛藏係身體對強權崇拜嘅基因<br />\n一日比一日腿張得更開<br />\n終有日會自願配合為虎作倀<br />\n香港自由行，零售，金鋪，藥房就係好例子<br />\n<br />\n唔想變成咁<br />\n<br />\n要牢牢記住一句話<br />\n中囯好，香港差<br />\n中囯差，香港好<br />\n深化到日常生活之中<br />\n<br />\n仲記得當年港元強勢兌一百幾十人仔嘅年代嗎<br />\n如果呢個係全香港市民嘅願望<br />\n就一齊努力令佢成真"},{"pid":"7de172f0a5651c5e30867680dc15da7afbbca3df","tid":2234322,"uid":370501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T23:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b30e0371f943d6d5f59fe12bbc0fd632880664","tid":2234322,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7de172f0a5651c5e30867680dc15da7afbbca3df","tid":2234322,"uid":370501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T23:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T23:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89047ea618eb070406ac883cf927cfa2e5d88b5b","tid":2234322,"uid":23833,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T23:18:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d86cc2ede6ba7b9365b65ebb2fdea3fdb52b112","tid":2234322,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T23:22:08.000Z","msg":"幾時都話要香港經濟收皮 股樓齊爆先會衝出嚟搏命"},{"pid":"bdfb2436a44324dae403e821608ccd673b6287d2","tid":2234322,"uid":191338,"li